snippet.title: Plug n Play Games: Spongebob Bikini Bottom 500 Racing
snippet.description:
Help support the channel: https://www.patreon.com/ZCInfinity
Review: http://zc-infinity.blogspot.com/2016/07/plug-n-play-tv-game-corner-spongebob.html

Gameplay footage of Spongebob Squarepants Bikini Bottom 500 Racing, a watered down Mario Kart clone that has surprisingly advanced graphics for a Plug n Play console.

Find more reviews of Plug n Play games at http://zc-infinity.blogspot.com
